<sentence id="2">The initial statistical analysis identified four differentially expressed virulence genes ( Tables 1 and 2 ) .</sentence>
<sentence id="3">Genes encoding streptolysin O ( slo or spy0167 ) and the SpeB protease ( spy2039 ) were downregulated , while genes encoding pyrogenic exotoxin H ( speH or spy1008 ) and a putative fibronectin-binding protein ( spy0130 ) were upregulated .</sentence>
