<sentence id="16">SpeB downregulation also coincides with increased expression of pyrogenic exotoxins [ 33,37 ] that reportedly increase streptococcal survival in vivo .</sentence>
<sentence id="17">We observed that the exotoxin-encoding speH gene [ 38 ] was upregulated .</sentence>
